k</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-no"><a href="https://no.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yasunari_Kawabata" title="Yasunari Kawabata — norvégien bokmål" lang="nb" hreflang="nb" class="interlanguage-link-target">Norsk bokmål</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-oc"><a href="https://oc.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yasunari_Kawabata" title="Yasunari Kawabata — occitan" lang="oc" hreflang="oc" class="interlanguage-link-target">Occitan</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-pa"><a href="https://pa.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E0%A8%AF%E0%A8%BE%E0%A8%B8%E0%A9%82%E0%A8%A8%E0%A8%BE%E0%A8%B0%E0%A9%80_%E0%A8%95%E0%A8%BE%E0%A8%B5%E0%A8%BE%E0%A8%AC%E0%A8%BE%E0%A8%A4%E0%A8%BE" title="ਯਾਸੂਨਾਰੀ ਕਾਵਾਬਾਤਾ — pendjabi" lang="pa" hreflang="pa" class="interlanguage-link-target">ਪੰਜਾਬੀ</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-pl"><a href="https://pl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yasunari_Kawabata" title="Yasunari Kawabata — polonais" lang="pl" hreflang="pl" class="interlanguage-link-target">Polski</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-pnb"><a href="https://pnb.wikipedia.org/wiki/%DB%8C%D8%A7%D8%B3%D9%88%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%B1%DB%8C_%DA%A9%D8%A7%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%AA%D8%A7" title="یاسوناری کاواباتا — Western Punjabi" lang="pnb" hreflang="pnb" class="interlanguage-link-target">پنجابی</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-pt"><a href="https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yasunari_Kawabata" title="Yasunari Kawabata — portugais" lang="pt" hreflang="pt" class="interlanguage-link-target">Português</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ro"><a href="https://ro.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yasunari_Kawabata" title="Yasunari Kawabata — roumain" lang="ro" hreflang="ro" class="interlanguage-link-target">Română</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ru"><a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9A%D0%B0%D0%B2%D0%B0%D0%B1%D0%B0%D1%82%D0%B0,_%D0%AF%D1%81%D1%83%D0%BD%D0%B0%D1%80%D0%B8" title="Кавабата, Ясунари — russe" lang="ru" hreflang="ru" class="interlanguage-link-target">Р