ities/html/90334047">Base de bibliothèque norvégienne</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://aut.nkp.cz/jn20000603323">Bibliothèque nationale tchèque</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.worldcat.org/identities/lccn-n81-097752">WorldCat</a></span></li></ul></div></li>
